main event: A witness observed two luminescent objects in the sky over California on September 23, 1952.
interesting points: The objects made a sound similar to a soft breeze., The first sighting reported 11-15 objects in formation flying from North to South., The second object was seen much farther away., The observation lasted approximately 3 seconds., The conclusion of the report was that the sighting was likely migratory birds reflecting ground light.
